1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>먼저 EC2 선택부터</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 861px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/615f1b5af3c39c60987bdc6703e22b8d/f843c/img01.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 126.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/615f1b5af3c39c60987bdc6703e22b8d/77434/img01.webp 300w,\n/static/615f1b5af3c39c60987bdc6703e22b8d/411c4/img01.webp 600w,\n/static/615f1b5af3c39c60987bdc6703e22b8d/3acdd/img01.webp 861w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 861px) 100vw, 861px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/615f1b5af3c39c60987bdc6703e22b8d/a8a0d/img01.png 300w,\n/static/615f1b5af3c39c60987bdc6703e22b8d/dface/img01.png 600w,\n/static/615f1b5af3c39c60987bdc6703e22b8d/f843c/img01.png 861w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 861px) 100vw, 861px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/615f1b5af3c39c60987bdc6703e22b8d/f843c/img01.png\"\n            alt=\"img01\"\n            title=\"img01\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>난 Ubuntu가 편하여 LTS 버전으로 선택해줬다.<br>\n본인이 원하는 OS가 있다면 그것으로 해도 무방하다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 785px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/307d82ffc6d2bdfe152ce772b9bbac00/18baa/img02.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 136.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/307d82ffc6d2bdfe152ce772b9bbac00/77434/img02.webp 300w,\n/static/307d82ffc6d2bdfe152ce772b9bbac00/411c4/img02.webp 600w,\n/static/307d82ffc6d2bdfe152ce772b9bbac00/fb49c/img02.webp 785w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 785px) 100vw, 785px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/307d82ffc6d2bdfe152ce772b9bbac00/a8a0d/img02.png 300w,\n/static/307d82ffc6d2bdfe152ce772b9bbac00/dface/img02.png 600w,\n/static/307d82ffc6d2bdfe152ce772b9bbac00/18baa/img02.png 785w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 785px) 100vw, 785px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/307d82ffc6d2bdfe152ce772b9bbac00/18baa/img02.png\"\n            alt=\"img02\"\n            title=\"img02\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>그 다음은 인스턴스는 일단 프리티어에 맞는걸로 해준다.<br>\n서비스가 잘 되서 확장하는게 아닌 이상 일단 맛보기용으로 운영하기에도 스팩이 나쁘지 않다.</p>\n<p>키페어는 이 인스턴스에 접근할 때 쓸 공개/비밀 키를 생성하는 부분인데,<br>\n난 키 하나로 돌려 쓰는게 아니라 하나의 인스턴스 당 하나의 키를 소유하게끔 한다. (너무 당연한 이야기…-_-;;)</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 786px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/52a857dc0a75fd7c7d535230aba64e0f/d703b/img03.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 78.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/52a857dc0a75fd7c7d535230aba64e0f/77434/img03.webp 300w,\n/static/52a857dc0a75fd7c7d535230aba64e0f/411c4/img03.webp 600w,\n/static/52a857dc0a75fd7c7d535230aba64e0f/f6aa4/img03.webp 786w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 786px) 100vw, 786px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/52a857dc0a75fd7c7d535230aba64e0f/a8a0d/img03.png 300w,\n/static/52a857dc0a75fd7c7d535230aba64e0f/dface/img03.png 600w,\n/static/52a857dc0a75fd7c7d535230aba64e0f/d703b/img03.png 786w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 786px) 100vw, 786px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/52a857dc0a75fd7c7d535230aba64e0f/d703b/img03.png\"\n            alt=\"img03\"\n            title=\"img03\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>보안그룹은 가급적 제한된 IP만 제공하는게 좋다.<br>\n나는 일단 ssh만 열어뒀다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 779px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/39eef9e401ea33ad1841fc319a4d11b6/a3e85/img04.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 46.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/39eef9e401ea33ad1841fc319a4d11b6/77434/img04.webp 300w,\n/static/39eef9e401ea33ad1841fc319a4d11b6/411c4/img04.webp 600w,\n/static/39eef9e401ea33ad1841fc319a4d11b6/aa866/img04.webp 779w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 779px) 100vw, 779px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/39eef9e401ea33ad1841fc319a4d11b6/a8a0d/img04.png 300w,\n/static/39eef9e401ea33ad1841fc319a4d11b6/dface/img04.png 600w,\n/static/39eef9e401ea33ad1841fc319a4d11b6/a3e85/img04.png 779w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 779px) 100vw, 779px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/39eef9e401ea33ad1841fc319a4d11b6/a3e85/img04.png\"\n            alt=\"img04\"\n            title=\"img04\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>스토리지는 10기가로 되어 있는데, 프리티어는 30기가까지 가능하기에 30을 맞춰준다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1126px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/aee7c65e43899b7fb2c7aad1ba6862e8/600ec/img05.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 45.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"